iption><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 12:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/prophetic-asani-hits-winner-gwangju-stay-second-asian-champions-league-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>德国为中国企业提供更多投资担保</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/germany-issues-more-investment-guarantees-business-china-2024-11-27/</link><description>德国经济部的数据显示，德国政府对华投资的国家担保价值在经历大幅下降后，今年有所上升。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:42:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/germany-issues-more-investment-guarantees-business-china-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>教宗每周接见活动将于12月起翻译成中文</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/popes-weekly-audiences-be-translated-into-mandarin-december-2024-11-27/</link><description>教皇方济各周三表示，从下周开始，他在梵蒂冈每周公开接见时的教义也将被翻译成中文。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/popes-weekly-audiences-be-translated-into-mandarin-december-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国假期将焦点转向通胀，法国局势紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-27/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:18:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在曼哈顿唯一的选举胜利是在下东区的这个街区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trumps-only-manhattan-electoral-win-is-this-block-lower-east-side-2024-11-27/</link><description>唯一的例外是下东区的一个街区，这里曾经是苏联间谍朱利叶斯·罗森伯格和埃塞尔·罗森伯格的家。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:06:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trumps-only-manhattan-electoral-win-is-this-block-lower-east-side-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>小马智行 2.6 亿美元 IPO 衡量美国投资者对中国企业的兴趣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-robotaxi-startup-pony-ai-raises-260-mln-us-ipo-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国的小马智行周三表示，已在美国首次公开募股中筹集了 2.6 亿美元，这家机器人出租车初创公司的估值约为 45.5 亿美元，这是寄望于美国市场投资者情绪改善的最新进展。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 10:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-robotaxi-startup-pony-ai-raises-260-mln-us-ipo-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行在针对欧盟卡特尔 3340 万美元罚款的法庭诉讼中败诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-loses-court-challenge-against-334-mln-eu-cartel-fine-2024-11-27/</link><description>周三，汇丰银行在针对欧盟卡特尔罚款 3170 万欧元（合 3340 万美元）的诉讼中败诉，此前欧洲第二最高法院在这起旷日持久的案件中支持欧盟监管机构。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 08:44:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-loses-court-challenge-against-334-mln-eu-cartel-fine-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，10月份国外智能手机在华销量同比下降44.25%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/foreign-smartphone-sales-china-drop-4425-oct-data-shows-2024-11-27/</link><description>一家政府下属的研究公司周三发布的数据显示，10月份包括苹果公司iPhone在内的外国品牌智能手机在中国的销量同比下降了44.25%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 07:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/foreign-smartphone-sales-china-drop-4425-oct-data-shows-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国称国防部长董军接受调查的报道是“追影子”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-calls-report-that-defence-minister-dong-jun-is-under-probe-shadow-chasing-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国外交部周三在回应有关中国国防部长董军因腐败接受调查的报道的问题时表示，这“只是追影子”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 07:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-calls-report-that-defence-minister-dong-jun-is-under-probe-shadow-chasing-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车在新疆承受多年销售压力后屈服</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-exit-xinjiang-operation-with-sales-local-plant-test-track-sources-say-2024-11-27/</link><description>大众汽车周三表示，该公司将出售其在中国新疆的业务，多年来，该公司一直面临着越来越大的压力，要求其放弃在该地区的业务，该地区的人权组织记录了针对维吾尔族人口的虐待行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 07:15:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-exit-xinjiang-operation-with-sales-local-plant-test-track-sources-say-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国禾赛明年将激光雷达价格减半，预计将在电动汽车中广泛采用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-hesai-halve-lidar-prices-next-year-sees-wide-adoption-electric-cars-2024-11-27/</link><description>全球最大的自动驾驶激光雷达传感器制造商中国禾赛集团表示，计划明年将其主要产品的价格削减一半，这将导致该技术在电动汽车中得到更广泛的采用。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 06:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-hesai-halve-lidar-prices-next-year-sees-wide-adoption-electric-cars-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国拒绝评论被监禁官员薄熙来之子的婚姻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-declines-comment-marriage-son-jailed-official-bo-xilai-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国周三拒绝就被监禁的前领导人薄熙来的儿子与台湾人的婚姻发表评论，只是表示反对对此事的“恶意”猜测。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 04:47:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-declines-comment-marriage-son-jailed-official-bo-xilai-2024-11-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>